100
00:05:33.166 --> 00:05:35.877
♪ <i>Que sera sera</i> ♪

101
00:05:38.171 --> 00:05:41.049
♪ <i>What will be will be</i> ♪

102
00:05:50.517 --> 00:05:55.313
♪ <i>Now I have</i>
<i>children of my own</i> ♪

103
00:05:55.397 --> 00:05:57.732
♪ <i>They ask their father</i> ♪

104
00:05:57.816 --> 00:06:01.486
♪ <i>"What will I be?"</i> ♪

105
00:06:01.569 --> 00:06:03.988
♪ <i>"Will I be pretty?"</i> ♪

106
00:06:04.072 --> 00:06:06.408
♪ <i>"Will I be rich?"</i> ♪

107
00:06:06.491 --> 00:06:08.827
♪ <i>I tell them tenderly</i> ♪

